    &lt;CommentText&gt;Dear Anonymous 

Thank you for taking the time to post your comments.  We value all feedback as it helps us to continuously improve our service.

We are so sorry to hear about your experience with trying to get hold of your scan results and can appreciate the stress and anxiety this must cause.

We have escalated this to the senior team in this area.  If you haven't already had a response from our PALS office, please can we encourage you to re-contact our PALS team so that we can give you some answers to the points you have raised.  You contact our PALS team on 0161 206 2003 or via email to pals@srft.nhs.uk between the hours of 08:30 and 16:30, Monday to Friday.

Thank you
